snippet.title: Grapple Force Rena - 2018 Trailer
snippet.description:
A playable browser demo is now available at the link below!

http://grappleforce.com

We've been working closely with Tim Ashley Jenkins to make Grapple Force Rena into a full game! Rena can do anything with her trusty grappling bracelets - swing from ceilings, climb up walls, pick up and throw objects, pull levers, fight bad guys, and more! You can aim it in any direction with a mouse or analog stick, too! Where did this nifty little gadget come from, anyway? Perhaps we'll find out when the game releases later this year!

Grapple Force Rena © 2018 GalaxyTrail, LLC.
